<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<p class="text-accent font-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Work</p>
<h2 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl uppercase tracking-wide text-dark leading-[0.9] mb-6">Project<br /><span class="text-accent">Gallery</span></h2>
<div class="space-y-4 text-dark/60 leading-relaxed"><p>At Code Blue HVAC, we take pride in every installation, repair, and maintenance project we complete. Our gallery showcases the quality of workmanship you can expect when you choose Code Blue HVAC.</p><p>From residential AC installations and furnace replacements to commercial rooftop units and ductless mini-split systems, our portfolio demonstrates the range and quality of our work across the Las Vegas Valley.</p><p>Want to see more examples or discuss your specific project? Contact us today for a free consultation.</p></div>
</div></section>
<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-light">
